      "source_region": "div.problem-additional-text",
      "text": "A construction of Selfridge (see [786]) shows that there exists such a sequence of density $>1/e-\\epsilon$ for any $\\epsilon>0$.\n\nSee also [786]."
    },
    "statement": {
      "sha256": "94520644fbe9594550e0a2da3543607a808a672731fab8fa9e9b0d23ff4f6216",
      "source_region": "div#content",
      "text": "Is there a sequence $1\\leq d_1<d_2<\\cdots$ with density $1$ such that all products $\\prod_{u\\leq i\\leq v}d_i$ are distinct?"
    }
  },
